text: Jergetal or Jerge-Tal may refer to the following places in Kyrgyzstan: *Jerge- Tal, a village in Aksy District, Jalal-Abad Region *Jerge-Tal, Ak-Talaa, a village in Ak-Talaa District, Naryn Region *Jergetal, Naryn, a village in Naryn District, Naryn Region *Jergetal, Osh, a village in Alay District, Osh Region
title: Jergetal
